421
00:25:00,599 --> 00:25:02,468
He won't die,
but he'll be stupid like you.

422
00:25:02,534 --> 00:25:04,269
When I saw you put Xiaolong
on your shoulders,

423
00:25:04,336 --> 00:25:05,704
