00:42:24,842 --> 00:42:25,943
Shancai.

788
00:42:29,947 --> 00:42:31,716
Ah Si has something to say to you.

789
00:42:32,717 --> 00:42:35,553
Shancai, it seems Daoming Si
is in a bad mood.

790
00:42:35,753 --> 00:42:36,921
Who cares?

791
00:42:36,988 --> 00:42:39,724
He's invisible to me from now on.

792
00:42:40,291 --> 00:42:42,326
-Invisible?
-That's right.

793
00:42:42,493 --> 00:42:44,462
I won't talk to him again.

794
00:42:56,007 --> 00:42:57,075
See?

795
00:43:12,590 --> 00:43:13,724
Welcome.

796
00:43:13,791 --> 00:43:14,725
Thanks.

797
00:43:16,360 --> 00:43:18,096
Why aren't you resting at home today?

798
00:43:18,162 --> 00:43:19,263
You even came to work.

799
00:43:19,530 --> 00:43:22,100
Never mind. I'm not a homebody anyway.

800
00:43:22,166 --> 00:43:23,401
I should just come to work.

801
00:43:24,068 --> 00:43:25,636
Actually, I'm fine.

802
00:43:25,703 --> 00:43:27,004
Welcome.

803
00:43:27,105 --> 00:43:28,339
You can also order here.

804
00:43:32,510 --> 00:43:33,845
Sir, we'll go ahead.

805
00:43:36,581 --> 00:43:38,683
Hurry, or else Shancai would be
off from work already.

806
00:43:38,749 --> 00:43:40,451
You have to speak to her nicely today.

807
00:43:40,518 --> 00:43:42,420
You can't wear that expression
like she owes you money.

808
00:43:42,487 --> 00:43:44,122
She really owes me money.

809
00:43:44,889 --> 00:43:46,290
Young Master Ah Si,

810
00:43:46,357 --> 00:43:48,192
you came to apologize today.

811
00:43:48,292 --> 00:43:49,927
Please mind your attitude, okay?

812
00:43:49,994 --> 00:43:51,129
All right?

813
00:43:51,596 --> 00:43:53,764
You're hurt so you can't go
to the audition.

814
00:43:53,831 --> 00:43:55,133
I'm sorry.

815
00:44:02,039 --> 00:44:02,974
What's the matter?

816
00:44:05,443 --> 00:44:07,345
Isn't that the person who hit me?

817
00:44:08,713 --> 00:44:10,381
I'm sorry, Xiaoshun.

818
00:44:10,448 --> 00:44:12,016
I got you involved in this.

819
00:44:12,783 --> 00:44:14,552
Why did he hit me, though?

820
00:44:16,053 --> 00:44:17,221
Because...

821
00:44:19,724 --> 00:44:22,493
I think he likes you, right?

822
00:45:54,285 --> 00:45:56,287
